-- Yahoo Says it Acquired Admovate Mobile-Advertising Platform
-- B y   L i s a   R a p a p o r t
-- 2013-07-17T16:58:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-17/yahoo-says-it-acquired-admovate-mobile-advertising-platform.html
Yahoo! Inc., the biggest U.S. Web
portal, has acquired Admovate to gain mobile-advertising
technology.  Admovate’s products help marketers reach their desired
audience at the right time and place, Sunnyvale, California-based Yahoo said in a blog post today announcing the
transaction. Terms weren’t disclosed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
